							<div class="post">Each servo uses 1 data pin.<br /><br />Each stepper driver uses 2 (Step/Direction), 3 (Step/Direction/Enable) or 4 (Windings 1/2/3/4) pins.<br /><br />Four steppers will take as few as 8 and as many as 16 pins.<br /><br />16 stepper pins plus 2 sevo pins is 18 pins.&nbsp; You could even use an Arduino UNO.</div>
